data.description: Another H property presents this Lifestyle-centric living. This is the new center of South County. Millenia is a unique mixed-use hub that embodies the new shift towards lifestyle-centric living. Chula Vista is the second largest city in San Diego, and the first four-year University in the city is being built here in the community of the Millenia. This community has a blend of activities, ages, and all the perks of a thriving community, intelligently designed into several walkable city blocks — about the size of downtown San Diego.  This exquisitely designed three-bedroom, three-in-a-half bath, Tri-level home is in the heart of the new and up-and-coming Millenia Community in Chula Vista. It is located in the Skylar subdivision with approximately 79 detached homes. It comes with contemporary architecture and modern elegance. As you walk through the front gate of this home, you observe a beautiful pet-friendly green turf front yard with sizeable gray stone rocks, 35 1/2 by 35 1/2 square gray concrete patio stone, and four miniature green trees. A small table and chairs for great outdoor San Diego days. Immediately to the left is a spacious patio for entertaining or relaxing under the sun. The first-floor bonus room has many options, from adding another bedroom to a theatre room, workout room, yoga room, nursery, etc. There is a full bathroom on the first floor. The second floor's phenomenal open floor plan has a luxury kitchen, granite island/countertops, and stunning light fixtures. The second floor includes a small office area, a walk-in pantry, and a 1/2 bathroom. All three bedrooms and two bathrooms are located on the third floor, along with a washer/dryer room. The master bedroom has a walk-in closet and a delightful his/her master bathroom with a tub and separate shower. There are many windows throughout the home, and with all the natural lighting, white walls, and light flooring, this open floor plan home has a clean, serene feeling. You're within easy walking distance of parks, promenades, shops, restaurants, and the local market: Otay Ranch Mall, Von's, Walmart, Starbucks, McDonald's, and much more. Millenia's various districts offer a unique lifestyle experience with distinct character and conveniences. Here are more features the home is equipped with. An ADT advanced home security system, with a sensor on the front door, garage door, first-floor bathroom window, and motion sensor on the second floor. Tankless water heater, Whirlpool appliances, keyless entry pad on the garage, whole house kitchen cabinets, shaker panel thermofoil mission 5, flat panel prewire, led lights, stair rail system, horizontal tubing.  This is a must-see!!!
